e\" Key=\"161\" RefId=\"魯桓公十三年七月\" Term=\"魯桓公十三年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，七月。<AlignEnd Key=\"161\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"162\" RefId=\"魯桓公十三年十月\" Term=\"魯桓公十三年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬十月。<AlignEnd Key=\"162\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":763,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129822","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00025","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯桓公十四年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:08","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"163\" RefId=\"魯桓公十四年正月\" Term=\"魯桓公十四年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>十有四年，春，正月，公會鄭伯于曹。<AlignEnd Key=\"163\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"164\" RefId=\"魯桓公十四年正月\" Term=\"魯桓公十四年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>無冰。<AlignEnd Key=\"164\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"165\" RefId=\"魯桓公十四年四月\" Term=\"魯桓公十四年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，五，鄭伯使其弟語來盟。<AlignEnd Key=\"165\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"166\" RefId=\"魯桓公十四年八月\" Term=\"魯桓公十四年八月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，八月壬申，禦廩災。乙亥，嘗。<AlignEnd Key=\"166\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"167\" RefId=\"魯桓公十四年十二月\" Term=\"魯桓公十四年十二月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，十有二月丁巳，齊侯祿父卒。<AlignEnd Key=\"167\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"168\" RefId=\"魯桓公十四年十二月\" Term=\"魯桓公十四年十二月\"><\/AlignBegin>宋人以齊人、蔡人、衛人、陳人伐鄭。<AlignEnd Key=\"168\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":764,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129823","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00026","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯桓公十五年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:08","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"169\" RefId=\"魯桓公十五年二月\" Term=\"魯桓公十五年二月\"><\/AlignBegin>十有五年，春，二月，天王使家父來求車。<AlignEnd Key=\"169\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"170\" RefId=\"魯桓公十五年三月\" Term=\"魯桓公十五年三月\"><\/AlignBegin>三月乙未，天王崩。<AlignEnd Key=\"170\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"171\" RefId=\"魯桓公十五年四月\" Term=\"魯桓公十五年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，四月己巳，葬齊僖公。<AlignEnd Key=\"171\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"172\" RefId=\"魯桓公十五年五月\" Term=\"魯桓公十五年五月\"><\/AlignBegin>五月，鄭伯突出奔蔡。<AlignEnd Key=\"172\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"173\" RefId=\"魯桓公十五年五月\" Term=\"魯桓公十五年五月\"><\/AlignBegin>鄭世子忽複歸於鄭。<AlignEnd Key=\"173\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"174\" RefId=\"魯桓公十五年五月\" Term=\"魯桓公十五年五月\"><\/AlignBegin>許叔入于許。<AlignEnd Key=\"174\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"175\" RefId=\"魯桓公十五年五月\" Term=\"魯桓公十五年五月\"><\/AlignBegin>公會齊侯于艾。<AlignEnd Key=\"175\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"176\" RefId=\"魯桓公十五年五月\" Term=\"魯桓公十五年五月\"><\/AlignBegin>邾人、牟人、葛人來朝。<AlignEnd Key=\"176\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"177\" RefId=\"魯桓公十五年九月\" Term=\"魯桓公十五年九月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，九月，鄭伯突入于櫟。<AlignEnd Key=\"177\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"178\" RefId=\"魯桓公十五年十一月\" Term=\"魯桓公十五年十一月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，十有一月，公會宋公、衛侯、陳侯於衰，伐鄭。<AlignEnd Key=\"178\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":765,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129824","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00027","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯桓公十六年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:09","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"179\" RefId=\"魯桓公十六年正月\" Term=\"魯桓公十六年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>十有六年，春，正月，公會宋公、蔡侯、衛侯于曹。<AlignEnd Key=\"179\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"180\" RefId=\"魯桓公十六年四月\" Term=\"魯桓公十六年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，四月，公會宋公、衛侯、陳侯、蔡侯伐鄭。<AlignEnd Key=\"180\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"181\" RefId=\"魯桓公十六年七月\" Term=\"魯桓公十六年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，七月，公至自伐鄭。<AlignEnd Key=\"181\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"182\" RefId=\"魯桓公十六年十月\" Term=\"魯桓公十六年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，城向。<AlignEnd Key=\"182\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"183\" RefId=\"魯桓公十六年十一月\" Term=\"魯桓公十六年十一月\"><\/AlignBegin>十有一月，衛侯朔出奔齊。<AlignEnd Key=\"183\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":766,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129825","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00028","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯桓公十七年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:09","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"184\" RefId=\"魯桓公十七年正月\" Term=\"魯桓公十七年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>十有七年，春，正月丙辰，公會齊侯、紀侯盟于黃。<AlignEnd Key=\"184\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"185\" RefId=\"魯桓公十七年二月\" Term=\"魯桓公十七年二月\"><\/AlignBegin>二月丙午，公會邾儀父，盟于趡。<AlignEnd Key=\"185\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"186\" RefId=\"魯桓公十七年五月\" Term=\"魯桓公十七年五月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，五月丙午，及齊師戰于奚。<AlignEnd Key=\"186\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"187\" RefId=\"魯桓公十七年六月\" Term=\"魯桓公十七年六月\"><\/AlignBegin>六月丁丑，蔡侯封人卒。<AlignEnd Key=\"187\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"188\" RefId=\"魯桓公十七年八月\" Term=\"魯桓公十七年八月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，八月，蔡季自陳歸於蔡。<AlignEnd Key=\"188\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"189\" RefId=\"魯桓公十七年八月\" Term=\"魯桓公十七年八月\"><\/AlignBegin>癸巳，葬蔡桓侯。<AlignEnd Key=\"189\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"190\" RefId=\"魯桓公十七年八月\" Term=\"魯桓公十七年八月\"><\/AlignBegin>及宋人、衛人伐邾。<AlignEnd Key=\"190\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"191\" RefId=\"魯桓公十七年十月\" Term=\"魯桓公十七年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，十月朔，日有食之。<AlignEnd Key=\"191\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":767,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129826","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00029","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯桓公十八年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:09","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"192\" RefId=\"魯桓公十八年正月\" Term=\"魯桓公十八年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>十有八年，春，王正月，公會齊侯於濼。<AlignEnd Key=\"192\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"193\" RefId=\"魯桓公十八年正月\" Term=\"魯桓公十八年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>公與夫人姜氏遂如齊。<AlignEnd Key=\"193\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"194\" RefId=\"魯桓公十八年四月\" Term=\"魯桓公十八年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，四月丙子，公薨于齊。<AlignEnd Key=\"194\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"195\" RefId=\"魯桓公十八年四月\" Term=\"魯桓公十八年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>丁酉，公之喪至自齊。<AlignEnd Key=\"195\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"196\" RefId=\"魯桓公十八年七月\" Term=\"魯桓公十八年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，七月。<AlignEnd Key=\"196\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"197\" RefId=\"魯桓公十八年十二月\" Term=\"魯桓公十八年十二月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，十有二月己醜，葬我君桓公。<AlignEnd Key=\"197\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":768,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129827","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00030","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯莊公元年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:09","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"198\" RefId=\"魯莊公元年正月\" Term=\"魯莊公元年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>元年春王正月。<AlignEnd Key=\"198\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"199\" RefId=\"魯莊公元年三月\" Term=\"魯莊公元年三月\"><\/AlignBegin>三月，夫人孫于齊。<AlignEnd Key=\"199\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"200\" RefId=\"魯莊公元年四月\" Term=\"魯莊公元年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，單伯送王姬。<AlignEnd Key=\"200\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"201\" RefId=\"魯莊公元年七月\" Term=\"魯莊公元年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，築王姬之館於外。<AlignEnd Key=\"201\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"202\" RefId=\"魯莊公元年十月\" Term=\"魯莊公元年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬十月乙亥，陳侯林卒。<AlignEnd Key=\"202\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"203\" RefId=\"魯莊公元年十月\" Term=\"魯莊公元年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>王使榮叔來錫桓公命。<AlignEnd Key=\"203\"><\/Alig